<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ subject }}</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f3f4f6; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#374151;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f4f6; padding:24px 12px;">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:970px; background:#fff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px;">
  <!-- Body -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:24px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height: 16px; color:#374151;">

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 16px;">Hi Krost Sales,</p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 16px;">
        A client has just sent an additional message through the Booking Confirmation page regarding their upcoming appointment.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 5px 0; line-height: 16px;"><strong>Message Details:</strong></p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 16px; background:#f9fafb; padding:12px; border-radius:6px;">
        "{{ client_message }}"
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 5px 0; line-height: 16px;"><strong>Related Booking Info:</strong></p>

      <ul style="margin:0 0 5px 30px; padding:0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.7;">
        <li style="margin:0 0 5px 0; line-height:1.7;"><strong>Client Email:</strong> {{ email }}</li>
        <li style="margin:0 0 5px 0; line-height:1.7;"><strong>Booking Date:</strong> {{ date }}</li>
        <li style="margin:0 0 5px 0; line-height:1.7;"><strong>Location:</strong> {{ location }}</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin:20px 0 5px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        <strong>Next Steps:</strong>
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 0px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
        Please review the request and reply directly to the client's email if a response or change to the booking is required.
      </p>

    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:0px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height: 16px; color:#374151;">
      <p style="margin:20px 0 20px 0; line-height: 16px;">
        Best regards,
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height: 16px;">
        <strong>Krost Website Booking System</strong>
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>